<h3 class="bp-subtitle">Display the Calendar in a Printer-friendly format</h3>

<div class="bp-text">
<p>For all of the views of the calendar, a print option is available to display the view in a printer-friendly format.	Simply click the <span class="bn-input">Print</span> link at the top of the view and print the page using your web browser.	The layout of the printer-friendly page will depend on the calendar view you were using when you clicked the <span class="bn-input">Print</span> link.</p>
</div>